O caused by spin-orbit-coupling and orthorhombic\ndistortion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 May 2018 09:49:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Aug 2018 15:41:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-19"}
